She felt his strong arm arond her waist and his hand on her back.
She knew this bot was under her control and he would tell her 
anything she wanted.  She could get all the information she wanted 
from him without having to seduce half the crew.  

She purred softly as he kissed her. She pressed against him and held 
him tightly against her body. She purred and her whole body gave off 
a soft vibration. 

Incase she had to seduce any more crew members, she hoped they were 
all as easy as this bot, she thought.
